{"title":"雨中，军车南下","authors":["陈有才"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":8,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨中，军车南下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈有才"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那车灯在雨中闪烁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿透风穿透雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿透雨点溅起的水珠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是军车吗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我分明看见的是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一艘艘战舰乘风破浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去和洪水搏斗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那车上的红五星在雨中闪烁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把狂风暴雨甩在身后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一车车军人吗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我分明看见的是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一段段钢铁长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去把人民的大堤加固"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一辆辆军车远去了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随车而去的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是中南海的谆谆嘱托"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是铺满国防绿的祖国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是我整个中华民族！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}